{"tid":1094557,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple會出傳統式摺機？最新專利圖片曝光","createTime":"2019-04-06T11:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T14:07:45.000Z","uid":50534,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ee68161a5c474a9633b17168c041c1b036c55d2f","tid":1094557,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T11:33:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/04/06/applefeaturephone/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F04%2F06%2Fapplefeaturephone%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYqNZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=0da71076\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/04/06/applefeaturephone/mobile-phone/</a><br />\n作為 Feature Phone 的摺機曾經盛極一時，而現代化的摺機就再次進化，近期 Samsung 與華為推出的新產品，攤開來可變大熒幕平板使用。不過有傳聞指 Apple 將會反其道而行，開發類似以往 feature phone 式的摺機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據外媒《Patently Apple》引述 Apple 最新的專利權申請書，發現有兩張繪上摺疊式設計的手機圖片，一邊是熒幕，而另一邊則是輸入鍵盤。在提案者的欄位中，填上了 Apple 產品工程師 Kevin Robinson 與高級產品設計工程師 Houtan Farahani 的名字。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次 Apple 提出的專利權申請書除了設計外，也包含了產品材料，Apple 會利用到鈦金屬與鎂金屬以不同的樹脂材料，以實現極為輕量、可經得起屈折的外殼。另外 Apple 早前已申請了可屈折玻璃的專利。<br />\n<br />\n不過報道再次提及到 Apple 申請了專利，並不代表一定會研發成為消費者產品，實際都要留待 Apple 進一步的公佈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/6a0120a5580826970c0240a49ca7b5200b-800wi-1.jpg \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F6a0120a5580826970c0240a49ca7b5200b-800wi-1.jpg%20&h=4caa159a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/6a0120a5580826970c0240a478131e200d-800wi-1.jpg \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F6a0120a5580826970c0240a478131e200d-800wi-1.jpg%20&h=c79a742c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/6a0120a5580826970c0240a49ca7ac200b-800wi-1.jpg \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F6a0120a5580826970c0240a49ca7ac200b-800wi-1.jpg%20&h=3ceae201&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"621a69cd0d4365d0dc01deed8f720faf3578350e","tid":1094557,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T11:36:49.000Z","msg":"通街都係嘅設計都可以申請專利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2547f096158a0ee99b07e60ddcaf9a5a6d58a74","tid":1094557,"uid":223868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T11:38:31.000Z","msg":"玩番轉頭？"},{"pid":"f9a986a187f1e3e5b8c52144f65f557aab6d3dd8","tid":1094557,"uid":12628,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T11:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/twapple/640pix/20180112/BN01/BN01_004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20180112%2FBN01%2FBN01_004.jpg&h=5c34e266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://image.thepaper.cn/wap/image/5/520/575.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.thepaper.cn%2Fwap%2Fimage%2F5%2F520%2F575.jpg&h=a4c7e1f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"757eef04c263382593e4e51bdc1f1e9c9a8fc7fe","tid":1094557,"uid":221819,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"621a69cd0d4365d0dc01deed8f720faf3578350e","tid":1094557,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T11:36:49.000Z","msg":"通街都係嘅設計都可以申請專利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T11:40:55.000Z","msg":"差之毫釐 繆以千里呀<br />\n其實大家諗法一樣，做出黎既野可以好唔同<br />\n蘋果出個Apple Watch 雖然出面個個都做緊同樣既野，事實證明差少少，到用戶手已經差好遠"},{"pid":"65fec637b7742ee24f3ff6c68b581c8d88ec05f7","tid":1094557,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T11:41:39.000Z","msg":"apple 年中都大把專利"},{"pid":"0c2ca3f4141e3de9d7ad92372db96e978e387de6","tid"